{
  "texts": [
    "While the GPT has made considerable waves in the industry, there have also been a lot of sober commentaries, such as [38] questioning its creativity, [21] expressing concerns on its impact on education, and [19] arguing a potential ethical problem in academia.",
    "However, the effectiveness of GenAI as an educational tool depends significantly on how teachers guide student interactions with these systems.",
    "Given that different prompts can produce varying responses from GenAI, educators play a crucial role in shaping these interactions to foster meaningful learning rather than confusion or misinformation.",
    "The study's findings, indicating that GenAI responses often lacked depth and creativity, highlight the need for experienced educators to guide students in interacting with AI.",
    "Teachers can:• Encourage Specificity: Train students to ask more specific questions that are tailored to the particular context or region of interest."
  ]
}